DeviceHive,is,a,framework,for,machine,to,machine,communication,that,can,be,used,to,bring,connected,devices,into,the,Internet,of,Things,DeviceHive,provides,control,software,and,platform,specific,client,libraries,to,jumpstart,the,development,of,home,automation,remote,sensors,and,more,The,RESTful,DeviceHive,API,acts,as,a,protocol,for,real,time,information,exchange,across,connected,devices,Consumers,of,the,DeviceHive,API,within,the,DeviceHive,ecosystem,include,the,device,client,and,administrator,The,device,sends,and,receives,notifications,via,the,API,The,client,can,be,used,to,control,and,monitor,devices,and,may,use,the,API,in,order,to,view,device,status,process,device,notifications,and,send,commands,to,devices,The,administrator,parameter,has,full,API,access,and,is,in,charge,of,creating,and,managing,users,devices,and,monitoring,commands,and,notifications,DeviceHive,is,an,open,source,project,and,can,be,found,fully,documented,on,GitHub